            <p>The Howard Goddard Collection was donated to the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives in 1997 by Esther Brown. This collection came to New York University in January 2001 as part of the original acquisition of ALBA collections, formerly housed at Brandeis University.</p>
        </custodhist>
